data.description: Needing your new home before the holidays?  Here’s your chance so don’t miss out on your opportunity to own this quaint and quiet home that is one of the most conveniently located and well maintained homes on the market. This home offers unique privacy in the front and backyard, all within minutes of all Van Buren schools, shopping, HWY 64, I540, I49, and many other amenities. Immaculately kept home from top to bottom, with new paint and carpet throughout. Detached shop with utilities is ideal for endless projects for all you do-it-yourselfers. The backyard is perfect for your family gatherings, bbq’s, and so much more. Call your favorite local REALTOR and make your appointment today.
